items.title: Trump threatens to slap 25% tariffs on EU, says bloc was always meant to hurt the U.S.
items.description: U.S. President Donald Trump threatened to impose 25% tariffs on imports from the European Union, claiming that the bloc was formed "to screw" the U.S.
